    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技术问题、BUG反馈或聊天交流</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入企鹅群：975109596</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也欢迎加入我们的官方 Discord 社区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以在 Steam 商店页面的右侧侧边栏中找到 Discord 的直接跳转链接入口。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >休闲扮演游戏。您是一名快递员，每天要忙于整理和递送包裹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩一笔画小游戏——用一条连续线穿过所有可通行格子，从起点到终点，成功后获得包裹。 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把包裹整理完毕，再亲手送到地图里的客户手中，或许还能触发小故事。 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体力用完了就需要休息，满状态就又可以整理包裹了。  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/2960008069b99929d3310f4dcdc15779.poster.avif?t=1768272754\" width=374 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/2960008069b99929d3310f4dcdc15779.webm?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/2960008069b99929d3310f4dcdc15779.mp4?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全角色动画</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有趣的益智小游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >触发有趣的小故事</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/e74e4c62da8d6a470e5e2505360de1f4.poster.avif?t=1768272754\" width=374 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/e74e4c62da8d6a470e5e2505360de1f4.webm?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/e74e4c62da8d6a470e5e2505360de1f4.mp4?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小游戏玩法 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用一条连续不抬笔的线经过所有“可通行”格子，从起点到终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/3df76b7ea331d551162baca933e58d3d.poster.avif?t=1768272754\" width=374 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/3df76b7ea331d551162baca933e58d3d.webm?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/3df76b7ea331d551162baca933e58d3d.mp4?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
